    • Class fractal.Layer extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      -5915996459965340211L

      • Serialized Fields

        • palette

          Palette palette
          The palette the layer will use to color itself

        • location

          Point location
          The location the rendering will be centered around

        • zoom

          double zoom
          The zoom of the layer. High values zoom in, lower values zoom out.

        • screenResolution

          java.awt.Dimension screenResolution
          The resolution any images created will be drawn as

        • realResolution

          Point realResolution
          The length in real coordinates of the longest edge of the window being drawn.

        • bailout

          long bailout
          The bailout value of the layer, eg the value at which the layer's iterative rendering will bail

        • maxIterations

          int maxIterations
          The maximum iterations of the layer.

        • layer

          int layer
          The layer level. eg, a value of 1 would mean this is layer 1, which is on the bottom. This is included because the coloring methods that avergae over the layers given an opacity level wont work without it.

        • autoBailout

          boolean autoBailout
          whether or not the program will automatically calculate a bailout value. This is not recommended for high quality renderings. This is intended for use in deep zooms.

        • autoMaxIterations

          boolean autoMaxIterations
          whether or not the program will automatically calculate a maxIterations value. This is not recommended for high quality renderings. This is intended for use in deep zooms.

        • name

          java.lang.String name
          The name of the layer. This is displayed in the layer view of the fractal GUI and is used in the saving of files

        • opacity

          double opacity
          The opacity of this layer. 1 = perfectly visible, 0 = invisible

        • visible

          boolean visible
          Whether or not the layer is visible.
